        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 0f88cdaa-d784-4951-8696-ea3065cc6228).Image",
        "Description": "Thornbridge Manor has been inherited by horrible people and we need to make sure it is passed down to a good person. You should kill the Undertakere, wear his disguise, and bury Alexa Carlisle to hide the body. Then Emma Carlisle wants to take over the mansion when Alexa dies and Gregory Carlisle owns it, so we must kill both Gregory and Emma to prevent this. Finally, Mr. Fernsby has been working to hand the manor to Emma for a long time. With him dead, all of this can end.",
